apt install rlwrap gcc-multilib g++-multilib tmux terminator mingw-64 

rlwrap: Allows up arrow and backspace on netcat shell
gcc-multilib: For compiling -m32 c code
g++-multilib: for compiling 32-bit c++ code
tmux: terminal emulator like screen but better
terminator: terminal that allows to split screens etc..
mingw-64: compile code for windows
